<h3>Intro C# Final</h3>
<p>My final project for the intro to C# class was something that I just did very simply and quickly. The requirements had us keep track of many different fields. For my assignment I went with a friendship application. It took a lot of information, names, favorite color, tv shows, and much more. The only logic I added to it was essentially if they are a certain level of desperate for a friend, they are automatically denied. However, if they are moderately desperate, they are only accepted if their favorite color is green. Otherwise, as long as they aren't desperate then they are allowed to be my friend.</p>
